@Node Main "GTDriver.guide"



                           @{b}GTDriver V1.0@{ub}
                               by
                 Roberto Attias and Marco Zandonadi




   This document describes @{b}GTDriver@{ub} V 1.0, a driver for serial graphic
tablets and serial mice.



